Erica Rhodes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erica_Rhodes 0 Erica Rhodes (born April 5, 1986) is an American actress and comedian. She has been performing on A Prairie Home Companion since the age of 10 and appeared in several movies and TV shows, including Plague Town, 1,000 Ways to Die, and The Consultants. She has also guest starred on New Girl, @midnight with Chris Hardwick, and Modern Family. Erica_Rhodes ( born April_5_,_1986 ) is an_American_actress_and_comedian .
